title: Atagoal wa Neko no Mori (Atagoal - Cat's Magical Forest)
synopsis: Today is the Atagoal town carnival. Talking cats and human townsfolk are having a ball. Enjoying the party to the fullest is our hero, Hideyoshi, a big fat cat, who is always involved in any trouble going on in the town.
staff: [['Nishikubo, Mizuho', ['Director']], ['Kobayashi, Hirotoshi', ['Script']], ['Masumura, Hiroshi', ['Original Creator']], ['Yusa, Kumiko', ['Color Design']]]
